data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Eagle Mountain with seller financing! Just $3,050 per month for mortgage excluding real estate tax and insurance. We can also offer Flexible Terms. Bright 3-story, 5+ bedrooms, 3.5 modern bathrooms with a beautiful contemporary kitchen. Spacious 3,341 sqft. Generous lot 4,008 sqft! Built in 2021. Situated in an ideal location, convenient commute to nearby amenities and urban centers. You'll find yourself just minutes away from shopping centers, schools, and recreational facilities, making it a perfect choice for both you and professionals alike. Natural light floods the interior of this open-concept home! Residence offers a perfect blend of modern luxury and natural beauty. Seize this rare chance to own a magnificent home with easy seller financing.
